server.gui

Class ServerGuiController

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.gui.ServerGuiController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable, ServerEventListener

    public class ServerGuiController
extends Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable, ServerEventListener
    FXML controller class for server screen in javaFX graphic user interface, let the user start new server by enter correct server and database details, this class handle creating new server instance that's listening for clients requests. every event that occurred on server displayed on server log.
